        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Leviticus 3:3-4",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), and thus to make atonement for the prince on account of his sin. עזים שׂעיר, or שׂעיר alone (lit., hairy, shaggy, ",
        "children": []
